{"tid":1569082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱由九龍灣返嚟既p牌仔 有少少野想同大家講","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:39:26.000Z","uid":287384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f34009f713c1642cb23af63012ebb7b1403ba61f","tid":1569082,"uid":287384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"經過今日<br />\n終於知道班用口嚟勇武既人<br />\n真係會害死手足<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好只係識得口頭勇武<br />\n屌完人老母叫完人出嚟隻揪之後<br />\n人地一衝又第一時間跑走啦<br />\n之後又走住嚟屌啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好撚柒呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你冇裝得口罩<br />\n其他手足唔係咩<br />\n唔該大家學識救人同還拖啦<br />\n狗又驚藍絲廢老又驚<br />\n不如返去做冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n沖上去救人<br />\n同廢藍開拖<br />\n次次都係得幾個<br />\n十隻手指數得晒<br />\n其他人就係到拍片食花生口頭勇武<br />\n有撚用咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">條片仲可能害死手足</span></span><br />\n到時少個勇武就真係多撚謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家行動升級<br />\n<br />\n1.有人聊交打 <br />\n即刻開遮 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為勇武做人牆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.見到人拍片影相 <br />\n即刻出聲叫停<br />\n大多八卦街坊都會即刻收手唔影<br />\n繼續影既 <br />\n多數都係藍絲廢老<br />\n開遮擋鏡頭做人牆<br />\n之後就勇武回合<br />\n<br />\n3.平時大合唱尻叫<br />\n除左嗌<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲要嗌埋嚟緊既週任</span></span><br />\ne.g 915 東角道<br />\n<br />\n4.大合唱完<br />\n順便去連儂牆做文宣<br />\n有poster癡poster<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇poster就寫嚟緊週末好去處</span><br />\n<br />\n5.口頭勇武既<br />\n學識點樣抽水<br />\n見到有9沖popo沖過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲沖得前過你既<br />\n你就跑過嗰陣<span style=\"color: red;\">抽下水打一兩下再走</span><br />\n勇武同廢老開緊拖嗰陣<br />\n就係旁邊<span style=\"color: red;\">打幾下 伸佢兩腳</span><br />\n戰況可能有少少唔同<br />\n<br />\n6.勇武囝囝既<br />\n唔好同大家割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多錫你春袋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.阻膠當廢老藍絲論<br />\n遮牆入面發生咩事冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住黃金十分鐘<br />\n速戰速決</span></span><br />\n齋圍同屌係冇用<br />\n正如大家伯母都畀人係咁屌<br />\n又有幾多個真係上到令壽堂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和勇合一<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n各自努力<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n五大訴求<br />\n同香港人<br />\n都缺一不可！<br />\n聽日915 東角道見</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afd92a0ee408ed943e509e5505854d0cde9e9b1","tid":1569082,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75fc482bceb5bc1a02a73ef9841255fa6c870b5f","tid":1569082,"uid":287384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"推到和勇都行動升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db4a679b2b188a2e4547c76ae0f5dd9fefa8179","tid":1569082,"uid":287384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"推到和勇都行動升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"